Attribution
================================================================================

The package layout, fork-versioned spec subtrees, and Versioned* wrapper
pattern of this library are heavily inspired by Attestant's go-eth2-client
(https://github.com/attestantio/go-eth2-client), which is licensed under the
Apache License, Version 2.0.

In particular, the conventions for:
  * one Go package per Engine-API fork (paris, shanghai, cancun, prague,
    osaka, amsterdam) — go-eth2-client uses consensus-layer fork names for
    the same idea; this library uses the execution-layer names because the
    Engine API specification itself organises its documents that way,
  * co-locating per-fork structures, JSON marshaling, and SSZ codecs,
  * exposing a top-level spec package with fork-agnostic Versioned* accessor
    types that switch on a DataVersion enum,

are reproduced from Attestant's design. The data structures themselves track
the Engine API specification at https://github.com/ethereum/execution-apis
(see in particular src/engine/*.md and the SSZ transport draft in
ethereum/execution-apis#764).

No source code from go-eth2-client is copied verbatim; the implementations
in this repository are written independently against the Engine API spec.
